// ║     A.2.b PD Arrays (FVG/IFVG/BPR/OB/BB)     🔜 NEXT                      ║
// ║     A.2.c Structure (BOS/CHoCH/CISD/MSS)                                  ║
// ║     A.2.d Liquidity (PDH-PDL-PWH-PWL-PMH-PML + EQH/EQL + KZ H/L)          ║
